      "title": "\u2139\ufe0f About \u2014 BrainDead Face Segmentation",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# \ud83e\udde0 BrainDead \u2014 Face Segmentation\n\nFull face anatomy segmentation using MediaPipe landmark detection + SAM3 mask refinement. Produces per-region masks (skin, eyes, brows, lips, nose, hair, ears) plus a clean RGBA head cutout and socket-infilled UV-ready output.\n\n## Flow\n1. **LoadImage** \u2014 load a portrait or face image.\n2. **BD MP SAM3 Face Segment** \u2014 MediaPipe detects landmarks \u2192 SAM3 refines each region \u2192 outputs 25+ anatomy masks + RGBA cutout.\n3. **BD MP Face Infill** \u2014 fills eye/brow/lip sockets with a flat colour for UV-unwrap-ready skin maps.\n\n## BD MP SAM3 Face Segment \u2014 Key Settings\n- **angle** \u2014 `front`, `side_left`, `side_right` (changes which features are extracted).\n- **do_*** toggles \u2014 enable/disable segmentation per region.\n- **edge_refine** \u2014 `guided` / `matting` / `vitmatte` for hair-quality edge refinement.\n- **remove_background** \u2014 if True, also runs SAM3 head cutout (uses `head_prompts`).\n- **drop_eyes / drop_lips** \u2014 punch out facial features from the skin mask (default True keeps skin solid).\n- **neck_cut** \u2014 trim the neck from the head cutout mask.\n\n## BD MP Face Infill \u2014 Key Settings\n- **fill_mode** \u2014 `flat` (solid colour), `surround` (sample from surrounding skin), `inpaint` (diffusion).\n- **eye_mode** \u2014 `iris` (ellipse around iris) or `eyelid` (full eyelid region).\n- **fill_r/g/b** \u2014 flat colour to fill sockets (default white = 255,255,255).\n- **lip_mode** \u2014 `organic`, `contour`, or `plane`.\n\n## Outputs\n- **rgba** \u2014 RGBA head cutout\n- **debug_overlay** \u2014 colour-coded anatomy overlay\n- **head_cutout_clean** \u2014 clean cropped head\n- **socket_image** \u2014 skin with eye/brow/lip sockets filled (RGB, UV-ready)\n- **alpha_image** \u2014 socket fill result as RGBA\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** \u2014 created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) \u00b7 [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) \u00b7 [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) \u00b7 [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)\n"
      ]
    },
